# MuSiQue benchmark — regenerable artifacts excluded from git.
#
# What's regenerable:
#   raw/          downloaded dataset (~30 MB jsonl)
#   docs/         1,700 paragraph .md files written by prepare.py
#   _logs/        ingest + run logs
#
# What stays in git:
#   prepare.py, ingest.py, run.py    — runners
#   README.md, results.md            — docs
#   manifest.json, questions.json    — sampled question set + provenance
#   _results/*.json                  — actual measurement output
#
# To reproduce: run `prepare.py` → `ingest.py` → `run.py`. See README.md.

raw/
docs/
_logs/
